&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 class=&quot;subheadline&quot;&gt;About Brandon J. Broderick, Attorney at Law:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Brandon J. Broderick is a prestigious and forward-thinking law firm committed to delivering exceptional legal services. With a blend of tradition and innovation, we are dedicated to staying at the forefront of legal practice and technology. We care deeply about our clients and our employees and are committed to ensuring a supportive and inclusive environment where every team member can thrive and contribute to our collective success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1wq2n7j&quot; data-start=&quot;339&quot; data-end=&quot;359&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;361&quot; data-end=&quot;663&quot;&gt;Brandon J. Broderick, Attorney at Law is seeking a skilled and motivated Business Litigation Attorney to join our growing legal team. This role will handle a broad range of commercial and business disputes from inception through resolution, providing strategic legal counsel and strong advocacy on behalf of clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;665&quot; data-end=&quot;850&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate will possess experience managing complex litigation matters, strong analytical and writing abilities, and a proactive, client-focused approach to dispute resolution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;18w7bso&quot; data-start=&quot;852&quot; data-end=&quot;875&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;877&quot; data-end=&quot;2020&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;mypfrn&quot; data-start=&quot;877&quot; data-end=&quot;1019&quot;&gt;Manage a diverse caseload of business and commercial litigation matters from pre-suit investigation through trial and appeal, as applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;kzzqpl&quot; data-start=&quot;1020&quot; data-end=&quot;1131&quot;&gt;Draft, review, and argue pleadings, motions, briefs, discovery requests/responses, and settlement agreements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;q1ly1h&quot; data-start=&quot;1132&quot; data-end=&quot;1221&quot;&gt;Conduct legal research and develop litigation strategy for complex commercial disputes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;oj603r&quot; data-start=&quot;1222&quot; data-end=&quot;1341&quot;&gt;Handle all phases of discovery, including depositions, document review, witness preparation, and expert coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;g7l5w8&quot; data-start=&quot;1342&quot; data-end=&quot;1447&quot;&gt;Represent clients in court appearances, mediations, arbitrations, hearings, and settlement conferences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1wwtnmd&quot; data-start=&quot;1448&quot; data-end=&quot;1577&quot;&gt;Advise clients on litigation risks, business disputes, contract issues, regulatory concerns, and dispute resolution strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1lz64zs&quot; data-start=&quot;1578&quot; data-end=&quot;1694&quot;&gt;Collaborate with partners, attorneys, and support staff to effectively manage case progression and client service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;7nqmpu&quot; data-start=&quot;1695&quot; data-end=&quot;1802&quot;&gt;Maintain strong client relationships through clear communication, responsiveness, and strategic guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1203idz&quot; data-start=&quot;1803&quot; data-end=&quot;1912&quot;&gt;Participate in trial preparation, including exhibit management, witness preparation, and courtroom support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1tew60i&quot; data-start=&quot;1913&quot; data-end=&quot;2020&quot;&gt;Contribute to business development efforts, networking, and client retention initiatives, as appropriate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 data-s

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 class=&quot;subheadline&quot;&gt;About Brandon J. Broderick, Attorney at Law:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Brandon J. Broderick is a prestigious and forward-thinking law firm committed to delivering exceptional legal services. With a blend of tradition and innovation, we are dedicated to staying at the forefront of legal practice and technology. We care deeply about our clients and our employees and are committed to ensuring a supportive and inclusive environment where every team member can thrive and contribute to our collective success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Relationship Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a relationship-driven professional with a background in sales, account management, and/or high-touch client service to join our growing Client Service team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will serve as the primary point of contact for clients navigating their claims journey. As a key member of our front office, you are the face of the organization — building trusted relationships, driving claim progress, and delivering a high-touch experience that sets the tone for everything that follows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position offers clear career pathing and long-term growth opportunities. High performers in this role can advance into Senior Client Relationship Manager, Team Lead, Operations, or other leadership tracks within the organization. We are committed to developing talent internally and promoting from within.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you thrive in a fast-paced, metrics-driven environment, and take pride in delivering exceptional client experiences, this is an opportunity to build a meaningful and scalable career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and manage a portfolio of approximately 100 claims.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the dedicated front office relationship lead, providing proactive updates and high-touch service throughout the lifecycle of each claim.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive claim momentum by coordinating with insurance carriers, medical providers, and third parties to secure necessary documentation and move claims forward.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify coverage opportunities, damages, and recovery potential through detailed claims review.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open and manage claims, ensuring all filings and deadlines are met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and manage liens, balances, and related financial components with strong attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize Litify (Salesforce) to maintain accurate, up-to-date client records and performance metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with internal teams, providing updates and strategic insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain organized files to ensure claims are positioned for successful transition when necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in sales, account management, client success, or high-volume customer service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable managing a “book” of clients with accountability for responsiveness and follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills with the ability to build trust and confidently handle sensitive conversations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly organized with the ability to manage multiple priorities simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detail-oriented while maintaining a client-first mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivated by performance, productivity, measurable outcomes — and long-term career growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Compensation Range:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;

