&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Compensation Range:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$55,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$60,000 USD&lt;/span&

